{"tid":985222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吉普賽妹子任人揉奶捏腿！「新娘市集」驗貨完直接回家啪～","createTime":"2019-01-17T11:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T13:04:17.000Z","uid":212399,"like":342,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b740d61d2f7f037b6cba872a61c1cab9453b53","tid":985222,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"每個國家的風俗民情不同，以結婚來說，台灣是透過長時間的交往，再決定要不要步入禮堂、攜手共度一生，但接下來粉粿要介紹的這個國家，卻是公然舉辦「新娘市集」，任君挑選！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210574.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210574.jpg&h=84788b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舉辦新娘市集的地區就是保加利亞中部的舊扎戈拉市，該活動源起於當地吉普賽人的傳統，吉普賽的信仰觀念中，嚴格要求男、女兩性從小就不能互相接觸，因此，他們幾乎沒有什麼機會和異性互動～也因此，為了把握這個能和異性相處的大好時機，也就是新娘市集，女生都會打扮得非常漂亮、化上濃妝、穿上火辣的衣服～<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210586.jpg&h=19e443e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210584.jpg&h=5bc1449a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210576.jpg&h=c65d8c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果女孩子打扮的越漂亮、穿得越裸露、身材越好，就能以較高的價錢把自己賣掉，啊男生們會跟著媽媽一起來市集「挑媳婦」，他們不僅會跟女方深入聊天、瞭解她的家事背景，更會直接伸手觸摸、揉捏女生的身體，看看她是否體態完美、適合生育&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210588.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210588.jpg&h=0c6e51d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n說到這邊，你可能會問，這些女孩子怎麼甘願被當物品、賣出去內？原來是因為&hellip;這些女孩子大多家境貧窮，她們都是自願出售自己，來改善家裡經濟，更有的女孩子是為了讓哥哥弟弟有錢娶老婆，才來參加市集的&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210573.jpg&h=8ebd8252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2210/2210580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2210%2F2210580.jpg&h=df8b4a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然粉粿不太認同這樣的結婚方式，但每個國家都有自己的文化呀～希望這些女孩子們婚後都幸福！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/21839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F21839&d=dUlPXj5JBOIv%2Bq9kYmFrqIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=611fc4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/21839</a>"},{"pid":"eac78ed393114fcb485d932adcf42c9f2f587409","tid":985222,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3c8cd256f5aff182decca1b4f56b7a1bbf11c3","tid":985222,"uid":99700,"like":5,"dislike":27,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"我出1千"},{"pid":"a2acda88993acba15b6cb9208316bec0d4ad8892","tid":985222,"uid":13495,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"深入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffcd9c411766150fc52ad69e2428441acef9750","tid":985222,"uid":59511,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"求攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77e8dd37b28391377d780f1f8f3ba5654bb6a5c","tid":985222,"uid":11598,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"有無女女肯跟我嚟香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6655934f15cdc7ccbc587c918936b81812c7ee6","tid":985222,"uid":29080,"like":125,"dislike":3,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:03:07.000Z","msg":"娶完就走佬"},{"pid":"23001d89a1a6cf891fdcf97f634807f38be7edda","tid":